<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Distribution">Distribution</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="http://fr.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Flamant_rose&amp;veaction=edit&amp;vesection=2" title="Modifier la section : Distribution" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="http://fr.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Flamant_rose&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Modifier la section : Distribution"></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
